&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solution Design.&lt;/strong&gt; Recommends technical solutions to meet customer integration requirements.&amp;nbsp; Where standard solutions do not meet customer requirements or pose significant risks, develop and recommend alternative customer integration solutions.&amp;nbsp; Provides direction for overall document flow from end-customer to end-customer.&lt;/li&gt;
