&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Document transformation.&lt;/strong&gt; Identifies needs for document mapping.&amp;nbsp; Build and configure transformation services using internal integration tools to apply data changes, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creates test plans that meet customer requirements and sufficiently reduce support risks. &amp;nbsp;Drives execution of test plan with the customer, including validation of results of GHX Services applied.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Communicate&lt;/strong&gt; directly with customer technical resources or managers, as required, to coordinate and complete assigned tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp; Provides documentation deliverables as required for repeatable ongoing tasks above including Salesforce and/or Jira cases, technical specifications, requirements documents, workflow diagrams, technical summary, step-by-step training guides, and internal FAQ guides.&lt;/li&gt;
