&lt;li&gt;Promptly keeps leadership and direct team abreast and informed of all challenges or matters of significance and suggests alternative courses of action which may be taken. Take prompt corrective action where necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintains a favorable working relationship with all other company employees to foster and promote a cooperative and harmonious working climate which will be conducive to maximum employee morale, productivity, and efficiency/effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supports scheduling setup to align staffing assignments with travel arrangements and inventory project needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be responsive to team members to assist with travel related issues even during off hours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs other duties as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
