&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design multi-agent workflows for document processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement tool-use patterns and integrate MCP servers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize orchestration for scale and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
